WHAT A HOOT! Crews tasked with decorating the 75-foot Christmas tree now at New York’s Rockefeller Plaza were shocked to find an owl inside the massive Norway spruce.

DENIAL AND DEADLOCK: President Trump's chances to challenge the election are dwindling in several battleground states. And while the President refuses to concede, some government health experts are being told not to talk to the Biden team. ABC's Elizabeth Schulze reports.

CORONAVIRUS LATEST: Oxford has announced promising results from its vaccine clinical trials, making it a potential third candidate. Across the country, hospitalizations are up in 19 states, and Wyoming, where there is no mask mandate, has a positivity rate that tops 90%. ABC's Mona Kosar Abdi reports.
2020 NBA DRAFT: With a little more than a month till tip-off, the #NBADraft is more important than ever. Will Ganss has the highlights from round one.
